bug.short_desc: All demos overview shows wrong versions for current and devel

long_desc.thetext: Not a big deal, but I got confused on finding the current.

The current stable version is 4.1 as 4.1.1 has not been released. We always link the latests stable as current. When it comes to the devel version, it should show the hash-code of the latest commit to see when we have updated. A quick tests with the showcase seems to work for me. Did you try another app where it does not work?
But shouldn't 4.1 be current (as it is the currently deployed version) and 4.2 be devel?

Ah, sorry. I have missed the link and thought you were speaking of the demo urls like http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/
Ofc, you are right!
Again the http://qooxdoo.org/demos/all does not reflect the current situation as 5.0 should be current and 5.1 should be devel.
Hi Dietrich, thanks for pointing out (again). Fixed the wiki page, but this time also added a recurring task to the release docs (5.0.x and master).
